cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with learning image features and their application to location and time estimation. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a method for implicitly learning features. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with learning features related to when and where an image was captured. 
4. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper deals with location and time estimation, which are important for image retrieval. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with image features and their application to location and time estimation, which are important for multimedia applications.
